---
source: crates/runtime/tests/metadata/mod.rs
expression: explain_met_last_modified_filtered
---
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: met_last_modified.id ASC NULLS LAST, met_last_modified.last_modified ASC NULLS LAST                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |   BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |     TableScan: met_last_modified projection=[id, value, year, month, day, last_modified], full_filters=[met_last_modified.last_modified = TimestampMicrosecond(1728538620000000, Some("UTC"))]                                                        |
| physical_plan | SortExec: expr=[id@0 ASC NULLS LAST, last_modified@5 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[false]                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |   BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |     DataSourceExec: file_groups={1 group: [[hive_partitioned_data/year=2023/month=2/day=2/data_1.parquet, hive_partitioned_data/year=2023/month=4/day=1/data_3.parquet]]}, projection=[id, value, year, month, day, last_modified], file_type=parquet |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
